the result of any kind of planning history, is

08:49.289 --> 09:03.291
where is it now, where has it been in relation to 
that. I think planning has had its difficulty in

09:03.980 --> 09:08.285
non-traditions due to the structure of 
government. That an effective business manager,

09:10.108 --> 09:22.443
that is a city manager,

09:10.108 --> 09:22.443
is bottom line results dollar oriented. Short 
term. Which means short term. Immediate. Right.

09:27.730 --> 09:29.051
